ort to PAAMAYIM NEKUDOTAYIM in PHP Version < 5.3</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 2.1.0 - Released: Jul, 29 - 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Frontend classes option panel</li>\n    <li>Added: yith_wcan_ajax_frontend_classes filter</li>\n    <li>Added: plugin works in product category page</li>\n    <li>Added: Select tags to use in filter</li>\n    <li>Added: WPML and String translation support</li>\n    <li>Updated: language pot file</li>\n    <li>Updated: Italian translation</li>\n    <li>Tweak: Shop uri management</li>\n    <li>Fixed: in stock/on sale works only with all option enable</li>\n    <li>Fixed: wrong filter link in product category page</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Widget filter by tag does not combine properly filters</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Widget doesn\'t work fine in Shop Category Page</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Remove trailing slash in widget shop uri</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Prevent double instance in singleton class</li>\n    <li>Fixed: The widget doesn\'t work with WPML with Label, Color and BiColor style</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 2.0.4 - Released: July, 13 - 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Filter \'yith_wcan_product_taxonomy_type\' to widget product tax type</li>\n    <li>Tweak: YITH WooCommerce Brands Add-on support in taxonomy page</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 2.0.3 - Released: July, 03 - 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Added: Support to Sortable attribute</li>\n    <li>Tweak: Yithemes Themes support</li>\n    <li>Fixed: Color lost after change widget style</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 2.0.0 - Released on Jun 24, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n    <li>Initial Release</li>\n</ul>\n\n  \";}', 'no');
